---

<Layout 
  title="Data Analytics - Cloud Intelligence"
  description="Transform your business data into actionable insights with comprehensive analytics, real-time dashboards, and predictive intelligence."
  keywords="data analytics, business intelligence, data visualization, predictive analytics, real-time dashboards, KPI tracking"
>
  <PageHero 
    title="Data Analytics"
    subtitle="Intelligence That Drives Decisions"
    description="Turn your data into your competitive advantage with advanced analytics, real-time insights, and predictive intelligence that powers smarter business decisions."
  />

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro-content">
        <h2>From Data to Decisions in Real-Time</h2>
        <p>
          Our comprehensive data analytics platform transforms raw data into actionable intelligence. 
          From real-time dashboards to predictive modeling, we help organizations make data-driven 
          decisions that accelerate growth and optimize performance across every business function.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="features-grid">
        {features.map((feature) => (
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">{feature.icon}</div>
            <h3>{feature.title}</h3>
            <p>{feature.description}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="process-section">
        <h2>Our Analytics Process</h2>
        <div class="process-grid">
          {analyticsProcess.map((process, index) => (
            <div class="process-card">
              <div class="process-step">{process.step}</div>
              <div class="process-icon">{process.icon}</div>
              <h4>{process.title}</h4>
              <p>{process.description}</p>
              {index < analyticsProcess.length - 1 && <div class="process-arrow">‚Üí</div>}
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="use-cases-section">
        <h2>Proven Use Cases</h2>
        <div class="use-cases-grid">
          {useCases.map((useCase) => (
            <div class="use-case-card">
              <div class="use-case-header" style={`border-left: 4px solid ${useCase.color}`}>
                <h3>{useCase.title}</h3>
                <p>{useCase.description}</p>
              </div>
              <div class="metrics-list">
                {useCase.metrics.map((metric) => (
                  <div class="metric-item">
                    <span class="metric-icon" style={`color: ${useCase.color}`}>‚úì</span>
                    <span>{metric}</span>
                  </div>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="stats-section">
        <h2>Analytics That Deliver Results</h2>
        <div class="stats-grid">
          <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="stat-number">10TB+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Data Processed Daily</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="stat-number">50ms</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Average Query Response</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="stat-number">99.9%</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Dashboard Uptime</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <div class="stat-number">500M+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Records Analyzed</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="cta-section">
        <h2>Ready to Unlock Your Data's Potential?</h2>
        <p>Transform your business with intelligent analytics and real-time insights</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="cta-button">Start Your Analytics Journey</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="faq-grid">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What data sources can you integrate for analytics?</h3>
          <p>We integrate with virtually any data source including databases (SQL, NoSQL), cloud platforms (AWS, Azure, GCP), SaaS applications (Salesforce, HubSpot, Google Analytics), file systems, APIs, and real-time streaming data. Our connectors ensure seamless data flow from all your business systems.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How quickly can we see results from data analytics implementation?</h3>
          <p>Basic dashboards and reporting can be delivered within 1-2 weeks. Comprehensive analytics platforms typically take 4-8 weeks for full implementation. Advanced predictive models require 8-12 weeks. We prioritize quick wins with immediate insights while building toward more sophisticated analytics capabilities.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Do you provide real-time analytics and dashboards?</h3>
          <p>Yes, our platform supports real-time data processing and live dashboards with sub-second updates. We use streaming technologies like Apache Kafka and real-time databases to ensure your dashboards reflect the most current business state, enabling immediate response to critical events.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How do you ensure data accuracy and quality?</h3>
          <p>We implement comprehensive data quality frameworks including validation rules, automated cleansing processes, anomaly detection, and data lineage tracking. Our systems include data profiling, duplicate detection, and continuous monitoring to maintain high-quality, reliable analytics.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Can you build custom analytics solutions for our industry?</h3>
          <p>Absolutely. We develop industry-specific analytics solutions with relevant KPIs, compliance requirements, and domain expertise. Whether you're in healthcare, finance, retail, manufacturing, or any other sector, we tailor analytics to your unique business challenges and regulatory needs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What's the difference between your analytics and basic reporting tools?</h3>
          <p>Our analytics go beyond simple reporting to include predictive modeling, advanced statistical analysis, machine learning insights, and automated anomaly detection. We provide interactive visualizations, drill-down capabilities, and actionable recommendations rather than static reports.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

